Package de.fha.dpmi.modeling.bpmn.elements

Model Elements and Model Relations of BPMN Models

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Collaboration
    A single collaboration with participants and message flows.
    ConnectingObject
    Representation of a Connecting Object which is either a MessageFlow or a SequenceFlow
    FlowObject
    Representation of a Flow Object which is a Activity, Event or Gateway.
    Lane
    A lane is a SwimLane which is used to divide pools.
    MessageFlow
    A MessageFlow is a directed edge between Pools or FlowObjects in different pools.
    Participant
    A participant of a collaboration is depicted as a pool, where a pool is used to divide FlowObjects from one another, it might contain one or more Lanes.
    Pool
    A lane is a SwimLane which is used to divide pools.
    Process
    A single process, e.g. part of a collaboration.
    SequenceFlow
    A sequence flow is a directed edge between two flow objects inside a pool.
    SwimLane
    A SwimLane is either a Pool or a Lane used to separate FlowObjects from another.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CollaborationImpl
    Implementation of a collaboration.
    ConnectingObjectImpl
    Implementing base class for connecting objects.
    ConnectingObjectMessageFlowImpl
    A MessageFlow is a directed edge between Pools or FlowObjects in different pools.
    ConnectingObjectSequenceFlowImpl
    A sequence flow is a directed edge between two flow objects inside a pool.
    FlowObjectEventImpl
    Implementing class for an Event
    FlowObjectGatewayImpl
    Implementing class for a Gateway
    FlowObjectImpl
    Implementing base class for flow objects
    FlowObjectSubProcessImpl
    Subprocess Type
    FlowObjectTaskImpl
    Task Type
    LaneImpl
    Implementation of a Lane
    ParticipantImpl
    Implementation of the participant interface.
    PoolImpl
    Implementation of a Pool
    ProcessImpl
    Implementation of the participant interface.
    SwimLaneImpl
    Implementing base class for SwimLanes.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FlowObjectEventImpl.Trigger
    Defines how the event is triggered.
    FlowObjectEventImpl.Type
    Type of the event.
    FlowObjectGatewayImpl.Type
    Defines the split behavior of this Gateway.
